  <preface>
    <title>Preface</title>
    <para>This specification describes the requirements to manage terminology produced by a variety
      of organizations across the healthcare enterprise. A Terminology foundation is required that
      allows the enterprise to extend terminology standards and implement extensions in a timely
      fashion.</para>
    <para>This specification is intended to support healthcare organizations' standard terminology
      modules, value sets, and coding systems as well as local terms and equivalence
      mappings.</para>
    <para>A standard-based Terminology Knowledge Architecture (Tinkar) specification is necessary to
      support the operation of a variety of systems intended to deliver knowledge management for
      terminology to vendors, providers, and standards-development organizations like HL7. </para>
  </preface>
